OL,5, Bernie Ecclestone, the former boss of  
OL,6, Formula 1, has been given a suspended  
OL,7, sentence after pleading guilty to      
OL,8, fraud.                                 
OL,10,FThe 92-year-old did not declare more   
OL,11,Fthan #400m held in a trust in Singapore
OL,12,Fwhen asked by tax authorities in 2015. 
OL,14,FEcclestone has agreed in a civil       
OL,15,Fsettlement to repay almost #653m to HM 
OL,16,FRevenue and Customs (HMRC), a court    
OL,17,Fheard.                                 
OL,19,FHe was sentenced to 17 months in       
OL,20,Fprison, suspended for two years.       
